# Test Navigation - Simple MCP Test

This is a simple test automation to verify the LLM → MDC → MCP pipeline works.

## Description
Navigates to example.com and takes a screenshot. Simple test to verify MCP integration.

## Keywords
test, navigation, simple, example, verify

## Steps

### Step 1: Navigate to Example.com
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_navigate",
  "params": {
    "url": "https://example.com"
  }
}
```

### Step 2: Wait for page load
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_wait_for",
  "params": {
    "time": 2
  }
}
```

### Step 3: Take a snapshot
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_snapshot",
  "params": {}
}
```

### Step 4: Take a screenshot
```mcp
{
  "tool": "browser_take_screenshot",
  "params": {
    "filename": "test_result.png",
    "type": "png"
  }
}
```

## Expected Result
- Should navigate to example.com
- Should wait 2 seconds
- Should capture page snapshot
- Should save screenshot as test_result.png
